{
  "stem": "16345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I wanted to go to Palestine, which was illegal at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I had already signed up to-- to get on a boat to be smuggled into Italy and from there go to Palestine, and then I got a better offer.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Somebody told me I could emigrate to the United States, which was actually the country I always wanted to go to.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because everybody knows that the streets are paved with gold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I mean, it's obvious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nobody in Europe that I knew of, except maybe a few exceptions, who did not want to go to the United States, who did not want to go to America, as it was called.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I signed up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, a friend of mine-- Allen, whom I met in Garmisch-- he-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he had also survived concentration camp, and he signed up.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, hey, Henry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want to sign up to go to America?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say, all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll go with you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we hopped a train, went to Munich, and signed up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I was called before he was, and they-- they were going to send me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, I'm not going without Allen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So eventually in January 1948, after a stay in a children's camp-- which was actually supervised by the-- I think it was United States Committee for Care of European Children.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a United Nations agency headed by Mrs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Eleanor Roosevelt.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I have Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Roosevelt to thank for my being here, and the UN.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And where did you come?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we arrived in New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there several weeks, and it was a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
